      "acceptanceCriteria": "Benchmark problems from NAFEMS and ASME V&V 10 suite reproduce analytic solutions within 0.5%.",
      "rationale": "Standard NAFEMS linear-elastic benchmark problems and beam-bending analytic cases were executed. All results fell within 0.5% of closed-form solutions, confirming correct implementation of the element formulations used in the pedicle screw model."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Discretization error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
